Package pf.analytics Description

Provides classes for all analytics calculations.

The main class is Point which replaces Point which is badly implemented. Point implements most methods of Point.

Relations of Points is represented by Vector.

The last piece is Line, which copies some of methods of Line2D.

This class also contains default implementations of these interfaces.
